These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, pall-mall, cain
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, chestnut, aquamarine
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade, cola
1. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
3. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is in an even position##4
5. the cain-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| Cigar   | cain       | old-henry     | pall-mall    |
| Color   | aquamarine   | chestnut          | ebony   |
| Beverage         | tea | cola | lemonade |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, tulip, aconite
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, martial-arts, epic
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, train, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is the person who growsaconite##1
2. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
3. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
4. the person driving the train is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Flower    | marigold     | aconite  | tulip  |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | martial-arts | scientific    |
| Transport     | bike      | airplane    | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, lemonade
3 different pets are kept: pony, fish, horse
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, mexican, dutch
1. the pakistani is in an even position##4
2. the dutch is the person drinking coffee##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| Beverage          | coffee         | lemonade     | 7up   |
| Pet   | fish       | pony     | horse |
| Nationality         | dutch | pakistani | mexican |

