.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, ice-hockey, handball
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, zombie, epic
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, apricot, coral
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
2. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
3. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |       3       |
| Sport   | soccer | handball  | ice-hockey |
| Movie-Genre        | epic | zombie  | western |
| Color        | yellow | apricot | coral         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-5::.
3 different games are played: go, whist, monopoly
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, milk
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, lacrosse, soccer
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person playing go##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
5. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
6. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing go##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| Game   | monopoly | go  | whist  |
| Beverage   | cola  | sprite | milk |
| Sport           | lacrosse  | soccer    | tennis    |

