.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, disco, r&b
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, balloon-flower, orchid
There 3 different types of food: lime, eggplant, watermelon
1. the fan of funk is between the person eating watermelon and the person who growsorchid##2
2. the person who growsazalea is the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of funk is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
4. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Music-Genre    | r&b  | funk  | disco        |
| Flower       | orchid | balloon-flower | azalea |
| Food   | lime    | eggplant   | watermelon   |

