.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-7::.
City: paris, nizza, prague
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, chess, poker
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, airplane, roller
1. the person traveling to nizza is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person traveling to prague##2
2. the person playing poker is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3    |
| City   | paris | nizza        | prague |
| Game           | mah-jongg   | chess      | poker     |
| Transport         | roller | airplane | motorbike    |

