.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, november, july
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, bike, skateboard
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, comedy, horror
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is between the person driving the skateboard and the person who's birthday is in july##2
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching horror movies is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3       |
| Birthday    | march   | november | july       |
| Transport     | skateboard  | snowmobile  | bike |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | superhero  | horror       |

