.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-9::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, bellflower, dahlia
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, funk, country
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, engineer, manager
1. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the fan of ambient is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the engineer##3
4. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of funk##1
5. the person who growslily is between the photographer and the person who growsbellflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |       3       |
| Flower         | bellflower | lily | dahlia |
| Music-Genre   | country       | funk  | ambient     |
| Job           | engineer     | manager     | photographer          |

