.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-10::.
3 different pets are kept: turtle, goldfish, cat
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, airplane, van
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, apricot, light-blue
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the airplane is the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
4. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person driving the van##1
6. the person driving the van is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3    |
| Pet           | cat | turtle        | goldfish   |
| Transport   | airplane | van | ship    |
| Color   | light-blue         | ebony      | apricot |

