.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-11::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, april, june
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, emerald, lilac
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, cricket, sailing
1. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who likes grey##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2      |    3    |
| Birthday         | june | april      | may  |
| Color         | grey         | lilac      | emerald    |
| Sport   | lacrosse         | sailing | cricket |

