There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, mirinda
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, bike, snowmobile
1. the person drinking cola is the owner of the turtle##1
2. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |      3       |
| Pet         | guinea-pig        | horse  | turtle      |
| Beverage           | mirinda | 7up | cola |
| Transport   | bike        | skateboard   | snowmobile  |

