1. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
4. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Hobby    | singing        | gardening | woodworking     |
| Movie-Genre       | epic | disaster          | action |
| Flower   | poppy     | azalea          | aconite       |

