.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-16::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, begonia, sunflower
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, strawberry, zucchini
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, indonesian, pakistani
1. the pakistani is the pakistani##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
3. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the indonesian##1
4. the indonesian is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
5. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the pakistani##1
6. the person who growssunflower is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Flower         | begonia   | bellflower     | sunflower   |
| Food           | strawberry  | cabbage | zucchini |
| Nationality   | pakistani | indonesian     | argentine |

