.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-17::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, scientific, musical
House: art-deco, victorian, craftsman
There 3 different types of food: grapefruit, cabbage, radish
1. the person eating radish is on the far left##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is the victorian house##1
5. the craftsman house is on the right of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Movie-Genre     | scientific      | fantasy | musical |
| House     | victorian | art-deco      | craftsman           |
| Food   | radish | grapefruit  | cabbage    |

