.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-18::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, raspberry, artichoke
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, fisherman, bartender
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, romance, musical
1. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the bartender##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
3. the bartender is in an odd position##4
4. the accountant is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
6. the accountant is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |
| Food    | cauliflower | artichoke      | raspberry     |
| Job         | fisherman  | accountant | bartender        |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | musical    | fantasy |

