.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-20::.
House: tower, townhouse, farmhouse
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, lemonade
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, june, january
1. the townhouse house is between the tower house and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
7. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| House         | farmhouse      | townhouse | tower |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | fanta      | lemonade    |
| Birthday           | january      | september        | june       |

 